This a C version of code published in Ray Tracing in One Weekend by Peter Shirley (available at https://raytracing.github.io/books/RayTracingInOneWeekend.html)

This version features realtime rendering using GTK+ 3.0 library.

Version 0.2
Finished chapter 7. Antialiasing.
Added camera.c and camera.h. Moved all camera/viewport operations here.
Changed functions that used GdkPixbuf pointer argument to use Camera struct pointer instead
Added utility.c and utility.c. Moved some commonly used functions here.
Added image scaling with a window.
Changed press callback function to translate mouse coords to picture coords.
Added range checks in get_pixel, put_pixel.

Version 0.1
Finished chapters 1 through 6.